description:
RNA and protein expression of C/EBP homologous protein (CHOP) and 78-kDa glucose-regulated protein (GRP78)  
  The mean cycle threshold (Ct) value for each sample was normalized to the mean Ct value of GAPDH in the same sample.&nbsp;  
   The participants in the current study were recruited in two groups; 44 recently diagnosed MS patients and 53 control subjects. Differential gene expressions of C/EBP homologous protein (CHOP), and 78-kDa glucose-regulated protein (GRP78)&nbsp; were assessed by real-time PCR. To confirm gene expressions at the protein level, Western blots were performed on three samples of each group; MS patients and controls.&nbsp;

